                    <comment id="13143178" author="rcmuir" created="Thu, 3 Nov 2011 13:57:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch: in lucene this was only called by things like tests for the most part.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The spellchecker used docFreq as an existence check: I added a TODO here as there are better/faster ways to do this trunk with seekExact.&lt;/p&gt;

